RESOLUTION No. 28
Introduced by: O'Brien, King, Abbott, Aylesworth, Baird,
Bartels, Burton, Cash, Clere, Criswell, Culp, Engleman,
Haggard, Heaton, Ireland, Judy, Karickhoff, Lauer, Lawson,
Ledbetter, Lindauer, Lucas, Manning, McGuire, Miller D,
